reviewText: Son loves this DVD. Another hard to find one for his collection
On the time with season 13 of power rangers with great fun and delightful delivery.
My son loves the power rangers and enjoyed this video!
this is great for familys and power rangers fans you will love it

This is one of my fav Seasons from any Power Rangers along with MMPR, Zeo, Turbo, In Space, Lost Galaxy, Dino Thunder and  Super Megaforce :) it has so much in it and is a great Season for any fan wanting to check out one they haven't seen yet ^_^ it also has a 2 part episode with rangers from the past like Adam/MMPR Black Ranger, Tori/Blue Wind Ninja Storm Ranger, Kira/Yellow Dino Thunder Ranger, Bridge/Red SPD Ranger and Xander/Green Mystic Force Ranger called Once A Ranger Part 1 and 2 :)
Unfortunately waited too long to open package  too late to return.  Disc 1 was cracked and wouldnt play.  Discs 2-4 wouldnt play.  Not sure if Im speanding another $13.48 for a replacement.
got it and it plays well and I have all of the discks
Loves the  power Rangers  so will be definitely ordering  from this seller again :)
It was every bit as good as I hoped it. It met every one of my expectations
It's a great another great season of power rangers. Has a good story line to it.
